{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":55,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":null,"text":"带下去，看仔细。","tone":"平静","chapter":68,"line_start":6,"line_end":6},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_xi_men_yu","text":"那些东西若真的还在你肚子里，我赔你一条命，否则，你就白死！","tone":"淡然","chapter":68,"line_start":12,"line_end":14},{"speaker":"char_huang_shan_da_han","speaker_name":"黄衫大汉","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"已看过了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":68,"line_start":20,"line_end":22},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_huang_shan_da_han","text":"有没有？","tone":"疑问","chapter":68,"line_start":24,"line_end":24},{"speaker":"char_huang_shan_da_han","speaker_name":"黄衫大汉","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"没有，他肚子是空的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":68,"line_start":26,"line_end":26},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":null,"text":"好——","tone":"平静","chapter":68,"line_start":28,"line_end":28},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":null,"text":"在我面前说谎的人，就是这种下场，各位明白了么？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":68,"line_start":30,"line_end":32},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":null,"text":"各位现在莫非也不饿了？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":68,"line_start":36,"line_end":36},{"speaker":"char_a_fei","speaker_name":"阿飞","listener":null,"text":"穿红衣服的人……穿红衣服的人在哪里？","tone":"喃喃","chapter":68,"line_start":42,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_a_fei","speaker_name":"阿飞","listener":"char_long_xiao_yun","text":"原来是你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":68,"line_start":50,"line_end":50}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":56,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_long_xiao_yun","speaker_name":"龙啸云","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"这人竟敢在大哥面前撒野，罪已当杀！","tone":"苦笑","chapter":68,"line_start":82,"line_end":82},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_long_xiao_yun","text":"门外有条狗，你瞧见了么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":68,"line_start":84,"line_end":84},{"speaker":"char_long_xiao_yun","speaker_name":"龙啸云","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"好像是有一条。","tone":"陈述","chapter":68,"line_start":86,"line_end":86},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_long_xiao_yun","text":"若要杀这人，还不如杀那条狗。","tone":"淡然","chapter":68,"line_start":88,"line_end":88},{"speaker":"char_long_xiao_yun","speaker_name":"龙啸云","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"大哥说得是，这人的确连狗都不如。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":68,"line_start":90,"line_end":90},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_long_xiao_yun","text":"你呢？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":68,"line_start":92,"line_end":92},{"speaker":"char_long_xiao_yun","speaker_name":"龙啸云","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"我？……","tone":"慌张","chapter":68,"line_start":94,"line_end":94},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_long_xiao_yun","text":"他不如狗，你却连他都不如，狗见了他，也不会逃的。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":68,"line_start":96,"line_end":98}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":101,"line_end":155,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":null,"text":"你们肯和狗拜为兄弟么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":68,"line_start":102,"line_end":102},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_long_xiao_yun","text":"连他们都不肯，何况我……","tone":"冷酷","chapter":68,"line_start":106,"line_end":106},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_long_xiao_yun","text":"我看你和那条狗倒真是难兄难弟，不如就和它结为八拜之交吧。","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":68,"line_start":108,"line_end":110},{"speaker":"char_long_xiao_yun","speaker_name":"龙啸云","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"你……你……","tone":"恐惧","chapter":68,"line_start":112,"line_end":112},{"speaker":"char_long_xiao_yun_jr","speaker_name":"龙小云","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"这主意本是晚辈出的，却不想反而自取其辱，而且祸及家父，晚辈既无力为家父洗清此辱，本当血溅当地，以谢家父，只惜慈母在堂，犹未尽孝，不敢轻生……","tone":"认真","chapter":68,"line_start":114,"line_end":114},{"speaker":"char_long_xiao_yun_jr","speaker_name":"龙小云","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"帮主可满意了么？","tone":"痛苦","chapter":68,"line_start":120,"line_end":122},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_long_xiao_yun_jr","text":"你是想以这只手赎回你父子的两条命？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":68,"line_start":124,"line_end":126},{"speaker":"char_long_xiao_yun_jr","speaker_name":"龙小云","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"晚辈……","tone":"痛苦","chapter":68,"line_start":128,"line_end":128},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_long_xiao_yun","text":"看在你儿子的份上，你走吧，以后最好莫要让我再见到你！","tone":"冷酷","chapter":68,"line_start":134,"line_end":136},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_a_fei","text":"这酒是给人喝的，你不配！","tone":"冷酷","chapter":68,"line_start":150,"line_end":150},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_a_fei","text":"你若要喝酒，自己买去。","tone":"淡然","chapter":68,"line_start":152,"line_end":154}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":4,"line_start":156,"line_end":220,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_li_xun_huan","speaker_name":"李寻欢","listener":"char_a_fei","text":"这里的酒比外面的好，你若要喝，我去替你倒一杯。","tone":"柔声","chapter":68,"line_start":172,"line_end":174},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_li_xun_huan","text":"等一等！","tone":"厉声","chapter":68,"line_start":212,"line_end":212},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_li_xun_huan","text":"既然要走，就不该来；既然来了，又何必走？","tone":"认真","chapter":68,"line_start":216,"line_end":216},{"speaker":"char_li_xun_huan","speaker_name":"李寻欢","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"不错，既然来了，又何必走？","tone":"淡然","chapter":68,"line_start":218,"line_end":220}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":5,"line_start":221,"line_end":310,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_li_xun_huan","text":"你的刀呢？","tone":"认真","chapter":68,"line_start":246,"line_end":246},{"speaker":"char_li_xun_huan","speaker_name":"李寻欢","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"你的环呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":68,"line_start":286,"line_end":286},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_li_xun_huan","text":"环在。","tone":"平静","chapter":68,"line_start":288,"line_end":288},{"speaker":"char_li_xun_huan","speaker_name":"李寻欢","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"在哪里？","tone":"疑问","chapter":68,"line_start":290,"line_end":290},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_li_xun_huan","text":"在心里！","tone":"认真","chapter":68,"line_start":292,"line_end":292},{"speaker":"char_li_xun_huan","speaker_name":"李寻欢","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"心里？","tone":"疑问","chapter":68,"line_start":294,"line_end":294},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_li_xun_huan","text":"我手中虽无环，心中却有环！","tone":"认真","chapter":68,"line_start":296,"line_end":296},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_li_xun_huan","text":"七年前，我手中已无环。","tone":"认真","chapter":68,"line_start":322,"line_end":322},{"speaker":"char_li_xun_huan","speaker_name":"李寻欢","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"佩服。","tone":"认真","chapter":68,"line_start":324,"line_end":324},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_li_xun_huan","text":"你懂？","tone":"疑问","chapter":68,"line_start":326,"line_end":326},{"speaker":"char_li_xun_huan","speaker_name":"李寻欢","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"妙渗造化，无环无我，无迹可寻，无坚不摧！","tone":"认真","chapter":68,"line_start":328,"line_end":328},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_li_xun_huan","text":"好，你果然懂！","tone":"欣喜","chapter":68,"line_start":330,"line_end":330},{"speaker":"char_li_xun_huan","speaker_name":"李寻欢","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"懂即是不懂，不懂即是懂。","tone":"认真","chapter":68,"line_start":332,"line_end":332},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_li_xun_huan","text":"李寻欢果然是李寻欢。","tone":"认真","chapter":68,"line_start":342,"line_end":344},{"speaker":"char_li_xun_huan","speaker_name":"李寻欢","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"上官金虹又何尝不是上官金虹。","tone":"认真","chapter":68,"line_start":346,"line_end":346}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":6,"line_start":311,"line_end":370,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_li_xun_huan","text":"你本是三代探花，风流翰林，名第高华，天之骄子，又何苦偏偏要到这肮脏江湖中来做浪子？","tone":"认真","chapter":68,"line_start":348,"line_end":350},{"speaker":"char_li_xun_huan","speaker_name":"李寻欢","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"想来就来，想走就走。","tone":"淡然","chapter":68,"line_start":352,"line_end":352},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_li_xun_huan","text":"你还能走？","tone":"疑问","chapter":68,"line_start":354,"line_end":354},{"speaker":"char_li_xun_huan","speaker_name":"李寻欢","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"是不想走，也是不能走！","tone":"无奈","chapter":68,"line_start":356,"line_end":358},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_li_xun_huan","text":"好，请出招！","tone":"认真","chapter":68,"line_start":360,"line_end":360},{"speaker":"char_li_xun_huan","speaker_name":"李寻欢","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"招已在！","tone":"认真","chapter":68,"line_start":362,"line_end":362},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","speaker_name":"上官金虹","listener":"char_li_xun_huan","text":"在哪里？","tone":"疑问","chapter":68,"line_start":364,"line_end":364},{"speaker":"char_li_xun_huan","speaker_name":"李寻欢","listener":"char_shang_guan_jin_hong","text":"在心里，我刀上虽无招，心中却有招。","tone":"认真","chapter":68,"line_start":366,"line_end":366}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
